    <item>
      <title>德桑蒂斯将否决佛罗里达移民法案，称其过于软弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/desantis-to-veto-florida-immigration-bill-calling-it-too-weak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯表示，他将否决共和党主导的立法机构通过的一项移民法案，认为该法案过于“软弱”，并指责立法者削弱了打击非法移民的力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/desantis-to-veto-florida-immigration-bill-calling-it-too-weak</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 19:19:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
